<Base title="Project Takeover" description="Project takeover for the market success of your online shop – Shopware 6 development by Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">E-Commerce</p>
<h1>Project Takeover for the Market Success of Your Online Shop</h1>
<p>A project takeover is always advisable when a running project in e-commerce will not lead to its goal despite previously well-managed stages. External circumstances and rapid market changes are possible reasons. With Shopware 6 and our development expertise, we support you in ensuring that your business project is brought to a successful conclusion.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Planning and Implementation of the Project Takeover by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>A project takeover begins with a thorough analysis of the previous project phases, regardless of the current process status. We assess the progress, identify weaknesses and develop a clear plan for continuation. With Shopware 6 and our experience, we implement the project in a targeted manner — without data loss and with minimal time loss.</p>
<p>The focus is always on the goal: to successfully and on time position your online shop on the market. In doing so, we keep an eye on the budget and communicate transparently about every step.</p>

<h2>Stages of a Project Takeover</h2>
<p>When taking over a running project, we proceed systematically:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Defining roles:</strong> Establishing clear responsibilities for all participants.</li>
<li><strong>Recognising the vision:</strong> Understanding and validating the original project goal.</li>
<li><strong>Measurable goals:</strong> Defining concrete KPIs and milestones.</li>
<li><strong>Planning:</strong> Creating a realistic timeline and roadmap.</li>
<li><strong>Project management:</strong> Structured management of all work packages.</li>
<li><strong>Budget planning:</strong> Transparent cost overview and control.</li>
<li><strong>Resources:</strong> Optimal allocation of team and tools.</li>
<li><strong>Communication:</strong> Regular updates and clear coordination processes.</li>
<li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Seamless recording of all decisions and changes.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Project Takeover with Alignment to Various Industries</h2>
<p>Whether fashion, lifestyle, food, automotive or services — a project takeover is advisable in any market environment. We know the specific requirements of various industries and adapt our developments accordingly. In doing so, you benefit from our wealth of experience from numerous successful projects.</p>

<h2>Benefits of the Project Takeover by Hob by Horse for Your Target Groups</h2>
<p>B2B clients benefit from fast, professional solutions that do not interrupt their business processes. B2C target groups receive an online shop that meets their expectations and offers a convincing shopping experience. In both cases, the professional project takeover ensures that investments are not lost, but are led purposefully to success.</p>
<p>Would you like to better position your online shop on the market through a project takeover? Contact Hob by Horse — we look forward to your call or email!</p>
</div></div>
</Base>
